import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Exam01 from "./components/Exam01.vue"
import Box02 from "./components/ExamMessageBox02.vue"
import Field from "./components/ExamField03.vue"
import taobao from "./components/taobao.vue"
import login from "./components/login.vue"
import ExamForm from "./components/ExamForm.vue"
import ExamTabbar from "./components/ExamTabbar.vue"
import HelloWorld from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import navbar from "./components/navbar.vue"
import weixin from "./components/weixin.vue"
import Home from "./components/weiChat/Home.vue"
import xz from "./components/xz/Login.vue"
import product from "./components/xz/product.vue"
import xzHome from "./components/xz/Home.vue"
import cart from "./components/xz/cart.vue"
Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Box02',component:Box02},
    {path:'/Field03',component:Field},
    {path:'/taobao',component:taobao},
    {path:'/login',component:login},
    {path:'/ExamForm',component:ExamForm},
    {path:'/ExamTabbar',component:ExamTabbar},
    {path:'/HelloWorld',component:HelloWorld},
    {path:'/navbar',component:navbar},
    {path:'/weixin',component:weixin},
    {path:'/Home',component:Home},
    {path:'/xz',component:xz},
    {path:'/product',component:product},
    {path:'/xzHome',component:xzHome},
    // {path:'/',redirect:"/xzHome"},//redirect 跳转，当在地址栏输入根目录，直接跳转到首页 
    {path:'/cart',component:cart}
  ]
})
